sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    participant FE as Desktop App
    participant API as POST /trigger
    participant Auth as AzureAD Auth
    participant Ext as Extractor
    participant SQL as SQL Server
    participant PL as Polars DataFrame
    participant DW as DeltaTableWriter
    participant DB as Databricks<br/>Unity Catalog
    participant SQLite as SQLite Cache

    FE->>API: POST /trigger {country, stage, queries}
    API->>Auth: Validate JWT token
    Auth-->>API: AuthorizedUser (roles, countries)

    API->>API: Check permissions (can_trigger_sync, can_access_country)

    API->>Ext: create_job(country, queries)
    Ext-->>API: ExtractionJob (job_id, queries[])

    par Persist job metadata
        API->>DB: insert_job() to Delta table
        API->>SQLite: insert_job() for fast reads
    end

    API->>API: CalibrationTracker.create(job_id)
    API->>API: CalibrationTracker.start_step("sync_data")

    API-->>FE: 201 {job_id, status: "pending", tag}

    Note over API,SQL: Background Task (ThreadPoolExecutor)

    loop For each query (max 4 parallel)
        API->>Ext: execute_query(query_name, country)
        Ext->>SQL: SELECT ... FROM {table} (chunked)
        SQL-->>Ext: ResultSet (rows)
        Ext-->>PL: Polars DataFrame (chunk)
        PL->>PL: concat_chunks()
        PL->>DW: write_dataframe(df, query_name, country, tag)
        DW->>DB: CREATE OR REPLACE TABLE ... AS SELECT
        DB-->>DW: Table written
        DW-->>API: QueryResult {rows_extracted, table_name}

        API->>DB: insert_version_tag(table, version, tag)
        API->>SQLite: update_job(results, running_queries)
    end

    API->>DB: update_job_status("completed")
    API->>SQLite: update_job(status="completed")

    API->>API: CalibrationTracker.complete_step("sync_data")
    API->>API: advance_after_sync() → "copy_to_calibration"
    API->>API: launch_calibration_step(job_id, "copy_to_calibration")
